><div class="wst-header-content header&#95;notes&#95;content wst-header-notes-content wst-unknown-notes-content">
<p>First edition 1871
Children's book which is an indirect sequel to <i><a href="/wiki/Alice%27s_Adventures_in_Wonderland" title="Alice&#39;s Adventures in Wonderland">Alice's Adventures in Wonderland</a></i>.
</p>
