<div class="prp-pages-output" lang="en">
<span><span class="pagenum ws-pagenum" id="Title" data-page-number="Title" data-page-name="Page:Through the Looking-Glass, and What Alice Found There.djvu/13" data-page-index="13" data-page-quality="4" title="Page:Through&#95;the&#95;Looking-Glass,&#95;and&#95;What&#95;Alice&#95;Found&#95;There.djvu/13"><span id="pageindex&#95;13" class="pagenum-inner ws-noexport">&#8203;</span></span></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r15620827" /><div class="wst-center tiInherit">
<p><span style="font-size:182%;">THROUGH THE LOOKING-GLASS,</span>
</p><p><br />
<span style="font-size:144%;">AND WHAT ALICE FOUND THERE.</span>
</p><p><br />
</p><p><span style="font-size:83%;">BY</span>
</p><p><span style="font-size:120%;"><a href="/wiki/Author:Lewis_Carroll" class="mw-redirect" title="Author:Lewis Carroll">LEWIS CARROLL,</a></span>
</p><p><span style="font-size:83%;">AUTHOR OF "<a href="/wiki/Alice%27s_Adventures_in_Wonderland" title="Alice&#39;s Adventures in Wonderland">ALICE'S ADVENTURES IN WONDERLAND.</a>"</span>
</p><p><br />
</p><p><i>WITH FIFTY ILLUSTRATIONS</i>
</p><p><i>BY JOHN TENNIEL.</i>
</p><p><br />
